JAVASCRIPT TEST 0002

Description
This assessment evaluates the candidate’s ability to implement decreasing pattern structures and logical loop control using JavaScript. The solution should ensure correct spacing and alignment.

Program

Write a JavaScript program to print the following pattern:

1 4 6 4 1
 1 3 3 1
  1 2 1
   1 1
    1

CODE : 


let n = 5;

for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {

    // print spaces
    let row = " ".repeat(i);

    // calculate middle value
    let mid = n - i;

    // print decreasing numbers
    for (let j = 0; j < mid; j++) {
        row += (j === 0) ? "1 " : (mid + j - 1) + " ";
    }

    // print increasing numbers
    for (let j = mid - 2; j >= 0; j--) {
        row += (j === 0) ? "1" : (mid + j - 1) + " ";
    }

    console.log(row);
}
